  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type II diabetes mellitus patients who have received medical treatment for more than 3
             months

          -  Patients willing to sign written informed consent form

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients unable or unwilling to comply with the requirements of the protocol

          -  Females who are pregnant or nursing or females of childbearing potential who are
             unwilling to maintain contraceptive therapy for the duration of the study

          -  Life expectancy &lt; 6 months due to concomitant illnesses.
      </textblock>
